  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kad ta KUNGĀ Enge-\nlis tchohs Wahrđus us wiﬀeem\nIsraēta Behrneem bij runnajś/\ntad pazehle tee Landis fawn Balk-\nfui/ un raudaja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee noꞥauze tahs Weetas\nWahrđu Bokim/ un tee uppure-\nja tur tam KUNGĀM.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo kad Josuïis tohs Laudis\nbij utlaidis/tad bija Israēta Behr-\nni nogahjuschi/ikkatrs us fawn ee-\nmantotu Teeju to Seini usneint.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee Landis kalpoja tam\nKUNGĀM/zik ilgt Josuïis dsih-\nwoja/un zik ilgt tee Wezzajee dsih-\nwoja / kas ilgu Laiku pehz Josuïi\nbij dsihwojschi/ kas bij redsejscht\nwiﬀu leeju Darbu ta KUNGA/\nfo wiꞥsch pee Israēta Behrneem\ndarrijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet kad Josuïis Nunna\nDehis/ ta KUNGĀ Kalps bij no-\nmiris fintś un defunits Gaddus\nwezz buhdams/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad aprakke tee wiꞥnu\neeksch winna Jhpaſchuma Roh-\nbeschastimnat Eresā/us Eewra-\nima Kalneem/tam Kalnam Gaās\nprett Seemeli.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu arridsan wiﬀ tas\nAuguns pee jaweem Tehweem\npeeſikts bija/ tad zehlahs zits Au-\nguns pehz wiﬀneem / kas to\nKUNGĀI ne pasinne / nedś arri-\ndsan to Darbu / fo wiꞥsch pee J.\nfracta bij darrijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad darrija Israēta Behr-\nni/kast tam KUNGĀM ne patif-\nke/ un kalpoja teem Baālim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un atstahje to KUNGĀ\nfatvo Tehwo Deewu/ kas tohs\nbij no Egipetesistweddjs/ undsin-\nnahs zitteen Deeweem pakkat/\nno to Lauschu Deeweem/ kas ap-\nkahrt teem bija / un peeluhsfe-\ntohs/ un apkaitinaja to KUNGĀ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tee atstahje to KUNGĀ\n/ un kalpoja Baālam un\nAstarotam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad apslaitahs ta KUNGĀ\nBahrsiba prett Israēlu/ un\nnodeve tohs teem Laupitajeem\nRohkā/ kas tohs aplaupija / un\nwiﬀsch pahrdeve tohs wiꞥnu Ge-\nnatneeku Rohkā wiﬀsapkahrt/\nun tee ne warreja wairs pastah-\nweht preeksch jaweem Eenaid-\nneekeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiﬀur kur tee isgahje/\nbija ta KUNGĀ Rohka prett\nteem par kannu / ittin ka tas\nKUNGĀS bij runnajś/ un ittin ka\ntas KUNGĀS teem bij swehrejs / un\ntee tappe gauscht spaiditi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGĀS eezeble\nSohgns/ kas tohs isglahbe no\nwiꞥnu Laupitaju Rohkas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet tee jaweem Sohgeem\narridsan ue klanfija / bet mankoja\nzitteen Deeweem pakkat/ un pee-\nluhdse tohs/ahtri atstahje tee no ta\nJelka/ fo winnu Tehwt bij gabju-\nschi / klanjidant ta KUNGĀ\nBautlus/ ta ne darrija tee.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kad tas KUNGĀS teem\nSoh-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
